column1: SQ1 Personal Income Summary: Personal Income, Population, Per Capita Personal Income

1/ Midquarter population estimates by state are derived by BEA based on unpublished Census Bureau estimates of beginning-of-month population. Quarterly estimates for 2010-2018 reflect unpublished monthly population estimates available as of February 2018.
* Estimates prior to 1950 are not available for Alaska and Hawaii.
Note-- Thousands of dollars, seasonally adjusted at annual rates. All dollar estimates are in current dollars (not adjusted for inflation).
Last updated: September 25, 2018-- new estimates for 2018:Q2; revised estimates for 1998:Q1-2018:Q1.
